{"tid":2171730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶台灣被判定中資罰41萬 限6個月內撤資或改正","createTime":"2020-08-24T07:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T18:50:53.000Z","uid":337052,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4a8513675502b976842ccbb5245e392e1245ff","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:02:07.000Z","msg":"淘寶台灣被判定陸資罰41萬 限6個月內撤資或改正<br />\n最新更新：2020/08/24 14:44<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200824/1197x803_384862999031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200824%2F1197x803_384862999031.jpg&h=8176a1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經濟部投審會24日表示，淘寶台灣雖由英商克雷達分公司經營，但克雷達可被陸資阿里巴巴實質控制，從而判定淘寶台灣為陸資，裁罰新台幣41萬元。（<a href=\"http://圖取自淘寶台灣網頁taobao.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AA%E6%B7%98%E5%AF%B6%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81taobao.tw&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=db011f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自淘寶台灣網頁taobao.tw</a>）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者梁珮綺台北24日電）經濟部投審會今天表示，經調查，<span class=\"red\">淘寶台灣雖由英商克雷達分公司經營，但克雷達可被陸資阿里巴巴實質控制，從而判定淘寶台灣為陸資，裁罰新台幣41萬元，限期6個月內撤資或改正。</span><br />\n<br />\n投審會指出，阿里巴巴在克雷達公司持股未逾30%，符合現行「大陸地區人民來台投資許可辦法」，但依法令或契約約定，阿里巴巴可操控英商克雷達營運方針，認定具控制能力。（編輯：張良知）1090824<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008245005.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202008245005.aspx&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=65e3054c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008245005.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"d47f05efe5137557651f92fb9d5fc72fd1cd344a","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:04:33.000Z","msg":"陸資來台將逐層認定嚴審 經濟部三大修法方向出爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008170235.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202008170235.aspx&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=26517280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008170235.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"36b75cf98781aa2f7b7a1838b172cca4dfafef6f","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"禁陸資OTT來台未封網 愛奇藝9/3後變跨境收視<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008190223.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202008190223.aspx&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=5fc76554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008190223.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"515fb6cbbc45fd6045cc6bfe21b3a056ac1748cf","tid":2171730,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6f29115ac4ac4fa7ea11a1943b2532f6613dad","tid":2171730,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931b002718a90b15ea300606e6ee407d71b115b7","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"制裁中國"},{"pid":"9f20791d8977e6da20f563bdf121d17d1bef5d2b","tid":2171730,"uid":100155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"藍蛆/統戰5毛：藍綠一樣爛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3ec48a6cb9577275319c6588b21f838e422f9a","tid":2171730,"uid":255976,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"中國內循環都夠賺，洗鬼同外地做生意，一於塘水滖塘魚，封國。"},{"pid":"95c2e079354d0b1fa50603121467fa1535039e38","tid":2171730,"uid":266342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"睇個名已經知支那野"},{"pid":"6f12ac17c34bce4ffc947a653cb76bfc5eb07325","tid":2171730,"uid":106634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"罰41萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bf517baf849eb3ffa22add16ba2380265d0dfb","tid":2171730,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"十萬左右HKD 笑左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eaa679a2b76ff35c998d7ed031e27f0c7bdb84b","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32bf517baf849eb3ffa22add16ba2380265d0dfb","tid":2171730,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"十萬左右HKD 笑左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"限6個月內撤資或改正才是重點"},{"pid":"eb134e2a5a3690a5fec6b6381409df26faa2c303","tid":2171730,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:20:53.000Z","msg":"早就應該啦<br />\n台灣快D 趕走叛國賊返支国"},{"pid":"0778aced7cc600f2503712adbbe3d8a825a29d67","tid":2171730,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"罰得太少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70eda194b54070f838c5c17a13b7406dc0da0745","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be3ec48a6cb9577275319c6588b21f838e422f9a","tid":2171730,"uid":255976,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"中國內循環都夠賺，洗鬼同外地做生意，一於塘水滖塘魚，封國。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeVD33LU8AA8IR1?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEeVD33LU8AA8IR1%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=04a22df2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de1f6426133cfe607394b3060d5372bc3d91d0da","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"淘寶台灣雖由英商克雷達分公司經營，但克雷達可被陸資阿里巴巴實質控制，從而判定淘寶台灣為陸資，裁罰新台幣41萬元，限期6個月內撤資或改正。"},{"pid":"82b166881d84635faa8d8fe7f40134b036aaf192","tid":2171730,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"［防中國流行文化入侵］台灣禁止中資 OTT，「愛奇藝、騰訊條款」 9月3日上路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2162935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2162935</a><br />\n<br />\n騰訊旗下子公司 Riot Games 因屬100%中資公司，無法在台灣直營《英雄聯盟：激鬥峽谷》，港澳版將與台版分拆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2154341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2154341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中資來台投資 管控趨嚴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經濟部長王美花昨（11）日拋出中資投資管理趨嚴的信號，因應港版國安法上路，經濟部將修法加強審查「中資」，避開轉投資的稀釋效應，預計下周預告修正《大陸地區人民來台投資許可辦法》，最快第4季拍板。<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法通過後，各界均傳出該修改兩岸相關法令的聲浪；王美花昨天上廣播節目時強調，有關投資審查的資格，目前不至於直接將「港資」視為「中資」，但是經濟部將修正中資投資許可辦法，也會跨部會討論對「中資」、「港資」的定義。<br />\n<br />\n經濟部官員表示，依據中英聯合聲明所制訂的港澳條例，「港資」屬於「外資」，由《外國人投資條例》管轄，因此本次預告修法的草案將維持認定「港資」屬「外資」；若港澳條例不改，經濟部也只能針對個案加強審查。<br />\n<br />\n王美花指出，雖然經濟部認定的港資是「外資」，但是，在港版國安法通過上路後，經濟部看待「中資」、「外資」，會有不同的想法；且香港這幾日來局勢的改變，也讓各界有所警覺，確實應重新思考中資的定義，以更嚴格的標準來看待中資。<br />\n<br />\n王美花透露，本次修法主要有二大方向，一、中資持股超過三成的認定方式，擬改為「逐層認定」，二、過去若有軍方色彩的中資，經濟部就會特別嚴格審查，但中共實則黨政軍一體，未來會針對陸方黨政軍色彩的投資案嚴謹審查。<br />\n<br />\n根據中資來台投資許可辦法第3條，中資若直接或間接持有該第三地區公司股份或出資總額逾30%，將會被視為中資。<br />\n<br />\n經濟部官員表示，這部分條文將不會更動，但會新增解釋令，調整計算方式，加強審查。<br />\n<br />\n官員舉例，過去中資投資第三地A公司40%，A公司再投資B公司40%，則計算上中資僅有16%，不會被認定為中資；不過，未來將修正為，先認定A公司為中資，再認定中資A投資B公司，因此，B公司也超過30%的門檻，屬於中資。<br />\n<br />\n王美花同時表示，港資來台投資的身分認定，確實是一個複雜的問題，港版國安法對香港是嚴重傷害，也是香港未來發展的重要轉折點。"},{"pid":"af7c675841d07a7cd50202fc89a3101d045526da","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EcKJIl6U4AMY-JG?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEcKJIl6U4AMY-JG%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=3b21d1f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab2e5f2863680f2a50cd164cc87caf195db72570","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/2mmbPkM00IJwIUV/status/1286537717925343233?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F2mmbPkM00IJwIUV%2Fstatus%2F1286537717925343233%3Fs%3D20&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=c3d84a25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F2mmbPkM00IJwIUV%2Fstatus%2F1286537717925343233%3Fs%3D20&h=eef5db49\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/2mmbPkM00IJwIUV/status/1286537717925343233?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"b32a1c9cd18452b7abd048792247c17e550f96ab","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EcdN9gnXYAA3ju1?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEcdN9gnXYAA3ju1%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=75eddd83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f89f23348c6819c5762c17d250389f87e5d41a7c","tid":2171730,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb134e2a5a3690a5fec6b6381409df26faa2c303","tid":2171730,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:20:53.000Z","msg":"早就應該啦<br />\n台灣快D 趕走叛國賊返支国"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5ba7269287a11